# Keep host build artifacts out of the Docker build context so images build cleanly and
# (critically) the host-generated Prisma client/engine — built for darwin — never leaks into
# the linux image, which caused "Query Engine ... darwin-arm64" runtime crashes. (DRIFT #34)
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/tsconfig.tsbuildinfo
packages/api/src/generated
packages/*/src/generated
**/*.log
**/*.out
.git
deploy/bot.env
